Articles.Content: Guys, I recieved a Jeb plushie from a friend who knows I like KSP! YUS!
I demand that my computer won't let me upload images right now because it is glitching out!

Jeb would find a way, let the plushie do it.  I presume that a corporeal incarnation of Jeb would immediately be imbued with all the powers of the real one, perhaps with powers diminished as a function of the square of his distance from Kerbin.
